import React from 'react'
import Footer from '../components/footer'
import Icon from '../components/icons'

export function FooterContainer() {
    return(
        <Footer>
            <Footer.Wrapper>
                <Footer.Row>
                    <Footer.Link href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/bryange/" target='_blank'><Icon className="fa fa-linkedin" /></Footer.Link>
                    <Footer.Link href="https://github.com/bryange3" target='_blank'></Footer.Link>
                    <Footer.Link href="https://www.instagram.com/bryangephoto/" target='_blank'>Instagram</Footer.Link>
                </Footer.Row>
            </Footer.Wrapper>
        </Footer>
    )
}
